<head>STRING</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">弦</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>A THREAD WHICH one MOVES WHEN PLAYING a STRING INSTRUMENT.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The general word for a string of any kind, on any bow or any string instrument, is xián 弦.</p>
<p>2. Xián 絃 tends to be specialised on strings used on musical instruments.</p>
        </div>
